Class ExtractionResultCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.ExtractionResultCollection
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Environment, Part

    public class ExtractionResultCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    Information collections are used to collect sets of extracted information as ExtractionResults, for example from different module extractions, to be saved together. An ExtractionResultCollection can be a Part or an Environment
